*Drugde* sam čuo da je to dobro mesto za šetnju. (I have heard somewhere that this is a good place for a walk).

*Drugde* smo stigli podne. (We arrived somewhere around noon).

Čovek koji je *drugde* bio nije došao. (The man who was somewhere else did not come).

*Drugde* smo potražili pomoć. (We looked for help somewhere else).

*Drugde* ću tražiti odgovor. (I will look for the answer elsewhere).